The Interconnected Vessels: Data Bus (PIPELINES)

Signatures: Complex green or blue piping connecting various tubs.

Function: These are the communication channels between the biological hardware and the spiritual software. They distribute the cognitive load to prevent local "Congestion" or mental breakdown during the transition.

