The Immersion Tubs: Buffering and Refinement (STORAGE)

Signatures: Nude figures immersed in fluid-filled basins.

Function: These basins represent "Buffer Memories." The vital spirit is temporarily pooled here to be purified of individual "Noise" (Ego) before it can be integrated into the universal logic.

