The Cascading Flows: Recursive Logic (LOOP)

Signatures: Fluid falling from one level to another in a continuous stream.

Function: A recursive processing loop. Each pass through the cycle further refines the synchronization, moving the subject from a fragmented state toward a singular, unified intellect.

